A gefen dama: Daniel Sturridge yana buga kwallo a Liverpool a wasan da za a yi da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier ta Ingila a hannun Chelsea, inda ya buga kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya karɓi ƙwallo daga Xherdan Shaqiri da ta kai wajen yards 30 a cikin ƙwallon ƙafa na Chelsea, kuma ya ci 1-0.
Ya mayar da ƙwallo a gefen hagu kafin ya yi kusa da saman kwando.
Sai ya yi ta yawo daga nesa, ya kuma yi ta yawo daga ƙofar jirgin har zuwa ƙofar jirgin.
Ba da daɗewa ba, sai wani ƙofa ya ratsa ƙofar Kefas Arisabala, wanda ke da nisa daga tsibirin.
"Ya kasance mai son shiga cikin filin, kasancewa a kan ƙwallon ƙafa kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq koyaushe suna gwagwarmaya don ci gaba, don haka na yi gwagwarmaya don samun lokacin da zan iya", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kante tana zuwa ta yi mata wasa amma ban kula da ita ba sai na yi mata duka".
Chelsea ta yi nasara da ci 1-0 a lokacin hutawa bayan da Eden Hazard ya buga kwallo a minti na 25 da fara wasan.
Blue ya yi wa Mateo Kovacic wasa a cikin wasan, kafin ya yi tafiya a tsakiyar filin kuma ya gudu zuwa Liverpool.
Kovacic ya zo ya yi wasa a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya yi wasa da ƙwallo, ya kai Hazard gidan yari.
Hazard ya bar dukan masu tsaron ƙwallon kuma ya yi gudu zuwa saman benen da kuma hagu ya wuce Alisson Becker na Liverpool.
Liverpool za ta yi wasa da Napoli a wasan da za a yi a gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Laraba da ƙarfe 3 na yamma a filin wasa na San Paolo a birnin Naples, a ƙasar Italiya.
Za a yi wasan da 'yan wasan da ke Chelsea a wasan UEFA Europa League a ranar Alhamis da ƙarfe uku na yamma a birnin London.
