Wani manomi ya gamu da kisan wani alade a wani kasuwa a arewacin ƙasar Sin, in ji kafofin yaɗa labarai na yankin.
An gano mutumin da ake kira "Yuan" da jini a kusa da wani gidan alade a Liupanshui, lardin Guizhou, inda aka gano shi da ciwon zuciya, kamar yadda South China Morning Post ta ruwaito a ranar Lahadi.
Wani manomi yana shirin yin allurar rigakafi a kan garkensa a ranar 30 ga Nuwamba-Mayu, 2005 a birnin Xining da ke lardin Qinghai, a ƙasar Sin.
An gaya masa cewa ya tafi da kawunsa daga lardin Yunnan da ke kusa a ranar Laraba don su sayar da aladunsu guda 15 a kasuwa.
Washegari, sai ya ga cewa ta mutu, kuma ya ga cewa ƙofar gidan ba a buɗe ba.
Ya ce, "Na yi rashin lafiya kuma na kamu da jini a cikin babban alade.
Binciken jikinsa ya nuna cewa wannan alade mai nauyin fam 550 ne ya yi wa manoman ciwo kuma ya kashe shi, bisa ga abin da aka ba shi.
