Wayde Sims ya yi garkuwa: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson da ake zargi da laifin mutuwar shugaban LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wanda ake zargi da laifin kashe Wayde Sims, ɗan shekara 20, kuma kocin kwando na LSU.
An kama kuma an tsare Dyton Simpson, ɗan shekara 20, a wannan sansanin don kisan kai na mataki na biyu, in ji sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge
'Yan sanda sun nuna masa bidiyon da ya nuna yadda Sims da Simpson suka yi faɗa, kuma suka ce Sims ya rasa tabarau sa'ad da suke faɗa.
'Yan sanda sun kama gilashin a wurin da ake yin harin kuma sun ce an gano jinin Simpson a cikin gilashin, in ji WAFB na CBS.
Bayan an yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda cewa ya yi wa Sims mummunan rauni.
