Sashen 'yan sanda na godiya ga rundunar' yan sanda ta jihar Louisiana, da dakin binciken aikata laifuka na jihar, da 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Kudancin kasar da kuma mazauna yankin da suka taimaka wajen kama mutumin.
Shugaban LSU Joe Alleva ya yaba wa sashen shari'a na yankin "saboda ƙoƙarinsu na neman adalci".
Sims yana ɗan shekara ashirin.
Wani yaro mai kafa shida da kafa shida ya yi girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya yi wasa a kwando a LSU.
Yaron ya kai kimanin mita 5.6 kuma ya sami kudin shiga na 2.6 a wasan da ya gabata.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, kocin LSU Will Wade ya ce kungiyar tana cikin "bacin rai" kuma "ta yi matukar damuwa" da mutuwar Wayde.
Wade ya ce, "Wannan shi ne abin da kuke damuwa da shi".
