An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da masu fafutukar neman 'yancin kai suka yi ta gwagwarmaya da 'yan sanda, kuma da yawa sun shiga cikin zanga-zangar 'yan tawaye a farkon bikin raba gardama a Catalonia.
Taron 'yan tawayen da ke da sanduna a gaban masu gadi suna yanka ƙwai da fenti na al'ada, suna yin ƙura a kan titunan da ya kamata ya zama wurin shakatawa.
An yi ta yin faɗa a wasu lokutan rana kuma 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da sandunansu don su yi faɗa.
Sa'o'i da yawa bayan haka, masu neman 'yancin kai suna ihu suna cewa "Babu mantawa, babu gafara" yayin da 'yan Unionist suke ihu suna cewa "Ku ci gaba da zama 'yan ƙasar Spain".
