Wannan wuri ne mai ban tsoro a yankin 'yancin kai, shekara guda bayan an yi zaɓe a ranar 1 ga Yuli, wanda ya zama kamar doka ba ta da doka a Madrid amma 'yan Catalan suka yi bikin.
