"Ƙara yawan kudaden bincike na AI zai iya zama kyakkyawan farawa, musamman a lokacin da yawancin ƙasashe ke da nisa a baya a cikin Amurka, kuma muna kallon ƙarin nasarar AI" in ji Lee.
Ƙara kuɗi zai iya ƙara yiwuwar cewa ci gaba na gaba na AI zai faru a Amurka, in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna "AI Superpowers China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" ya fito a wannan watan tare da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin da ke da alhakin AI a China, Face++.
