Lokacin Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron da ya yi a wannan yammacin a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan taron yana ɗaya daga cikin taro biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, kuma zai yi a wurare da yawa da ke da tarurruka har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran tabbacin kuri'un da za a yi na neman kujerar kotun koli, Trump yana son ya kara goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa rinjaye a majalisar dattawa a lokacin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Wane lokaci ne taron Trump na West Virginia zai kasance a yau da kuma yadda za a fara a kan layi?
An saita lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia a 7 na yamma ET yau da dare, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a YouTube ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye.
An yi tsammanin Trump zai yi jawabi a kotun koli na wannan makon a kan shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi ta fama da zargin cewa ya yi niyyar gyara mata a lokacin da aka dage zaben tabbatar da shi har sai mako guda bayan FBI ta fara bincike.
Amma, yawan aikin da aka yi a taron ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi shiri sosai don zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, kamfen din Shugaba Trump na wannan makon ya mayar da hankali kan "karfafawa masu goyon bayan Republican da masu goyon bayan Republican damar karewa da kuma kara yawan kujerun da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Matsayin majalisa ya tilasta wa shugabanni su yi tafiya sosai yayin da muke shiga lokacin da ake neman masu jefa kuri'a", in ji mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump wanda ya ƙi ambata sunansa.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai kawo masu goyon baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma masu sauraro a tashar rediyo a Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan nan a jihar West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben 2016.
Trump yana neman goyon bayan Patrick Morrisey, ɗan majalisar dattawa na jam'iyyar Republican a West Virginia, wanda ya yi rashin nasara a zaben.
Simon Haeder, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia ya ce: "Ba zai yi wa Morrissey kyau ba idan shugaban ya zo ya taimaka masa wajen samun kuri'u".
