Turai ta yi nasara da ƙwallo 10-6 a ranar da za a kammala gasar Ryder Cup
Turai tana da dama sosai a ranar da za ta kammala gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta ci wasanni huɗu da huɗu a ranar Asabar kuma Amirka ta ci gaba da ci 10-6.
Wasu 'yan wasa guda biyu, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun kai Tiger Woods gasar cin kofin duniya sau huɗu a filin Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda take son ta sake lashe gasar da aka yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, ta yi nasara a kan 'yan wasan Amirka da suka yi wasa a wasan 4 da 4 na safe, da ci 3-1.
