Wata 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amirka mai suna Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ta saka wasu labaran 'yan majalisa uku na Republican a shafin Wikipedia na dokar.
Dan Democrat na Los Angeles ya ce "yan adawa" ne suka kafa wannan tunanin, wato masu yada labarai da kuma shafukan sada zumunta.
Waters ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Ƙarya, ƙarya, ƙarya ce ta gaske".
An ba da rahoton cewa an saka adireshin gida da kuma lambar waya na U.S. Sen. Lindsey Graham daga South Carolina, Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Wannan labarin ya bayyana a dandalin sada zumunta na Intane a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a kan Capitol Hill a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar da aka yi a majalisar dattawa game da zargin da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh da aka zaɓa a babban kotun da ake tuhumarsa da yin lalata da 'yancin bil'adama.
Labarin ya bazu ne bayan da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka kammala shari'ar Kavanaugh.
Shafukan yanar gizo na Conservative kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ce ofishin Waters ne ya tura adireshin IP da ke nuna wanda ya aika saƙon kuma ya ba da labarin wani mai amfani da sunan Waters, in ji wata jaridar Hill.
Waters ya ce: "Wannan ƙarya ce da ba a tabbatar da ita ba.
"Bawana - wanda kuka rikita alamomi, labari, da kariya saboda wannan yaudara da zato na ƙarya - da gaske bai yada wannan labarin ba.
