An yi amfani da kalmomin Waters a kan dandalin sada zumunta, har da jaridar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan rashin fushi ne", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan yana nufin cewa bai damu da kasancewa cikin Majalisa ba.
Idan aka yi wa mutum baƙar magana, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Bai kamata mu yi fushi don mu kāre kanmu ba.
Bai kamata ya tambayi wanda yake zarginsa dalilin da ya sa yake tsaye ba.
Ya kamata ta kasance da tawali'u da kuma haƙuri.
Fleischer ya yi ƙoƙari ya kwatanta fushin Waters da na 'yan Democrat game da Alƙali Kavanaugh, wanda masu sūka suka ce ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin shari'ar gaskiya.
Omar Navarro, wanda ke takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman kawar da Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Wannan babban abu ne idan gaskiya ne", in ji wani sakon Twitter.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya gargadi "masu hannu da kuma jami'an tsaro game da wannan zargin aikata laifuka.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa masu laifin sun kama su", in ji su, "amma kuma za a hukunta su saboda ayyukansu na halaka da kuma haɗari ga kowa da kuma ma'aikatansa".
Johnny English ya Sake Sakewa - Wasan kwaikwayo na Rowan Atkinson
A yau, al'ada ce a raba abubuwan da suka shafi Brexit a cikin sabon shirin da ke nuna tarihin Burtaniya da kuma sabon shirin da ake kira Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Zai iya kawo zargi mai ban sha'awa game da matsalarmu a matsayin ƙasa game da damarmu na fitar da kayayyakinmu?
Ko yaya dai, Johnny English mai ido mai kyau ya ƙara lambar sa ta farko a wasan kwaikwayo - sunan da ya nuna cewa shi mai wasan kwaikwayo ne da ya fi kowa a duniya.
Wani mai amfani da shi zai yi wasa da shi ta hanyar haɗa abubuwan nishaɗi kamar ƙaramin Mai Bincike, kamar Mr Bean da kuma wani nau'in mai ƙara murya ga waƙar Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗewar wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Da farko, ya dogara ga wani mutum mai tafiya sosai, Atkinson, wanda ya kasance a cikin wani gidan talabijin da aka manta da shi a zamaninmu, wanda ya yi watsi da dukan matsalolin da ya fuskanta.
Akwai abu ɗaya ko biyu mai kyau a cikin sabon tsarin JE.
Na yi farin ciki sosai sa'ad da na ga Johnny English yana zuwa jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da rigar soja da fuka-fukansa suna ratsawa a kan bututun jirgin.
Kyautar Atkinson ta wasan kwaikwayo ta bayyana, amma a wasu lokuta wasan kwaikwayo na iya zama mai rauni da kuma wasu lokuta fiye da yadda ya kamata, musamman ma lokacin da aka gabatar da wasan kwaikwayo na 007 da Mission Impossible.
An fi son nishaɗi na yau da kullum ga matasa fiye da manya, kuma yawancin abubuwan da Johnny English ya wuce ba su da wasu abubuwan da suka dace kamar yadda ya faru a cikin wasan kwaikwayon Atkinson a matsayin Bean.
Labarin wannan shekarar ya nuna cewa Biritaniya tana cikin mawuyacin hali.
Wani ɗan leƙen asiri ya shiga cikin asirin gidan yanar gizon 'yan leƙen asiri na Britaniya, kuma ya fallasa duk wani ɗan ofishin jakadancin Britaniya da ke wurare dabam-dabam, abin da ya ba wa wani da ke aiki a lokacin mamaki - aikin da Kevin Eldon bai yi ba.
Wannan abu ne mai wuya ga babban firaminista mai girman kai da rashin tsaro, wanda ke fama da raguwar ikonsa da kuma sanannun sanannun siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi nasara a matsayin mai wakiltar Theresa May amma ba ta da yawa a cikin jerin maganganun da za a yi amfani da su.
An umurci waɗanda suka riga su zama masu kula da su cewa duk lokacin da aka daina aikin masu bincike, dole ne a dawo da duk wanda ya daina.
Wannan ya haɗa da Johnny English, wanda shi ne shugaban makarantar, amma yana ba da darussa game da yin aiki a ɓoye: abin farin ciki, English yana koyar da koyarwar leken asiri a makarantar Rock.
An yi wa English fyade kuma an kai shi Whitehall don taron kwamitin kuma ya sake saduwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake kamawa.
Bough yanzu yana da aure, kuma yana tare da kyaftin din jirgin ruwa, mai suna Vicki Pepperdine wanda ya shahara sosai.
Saboda haka, abubuwa da ba za a iya kawar da su ba sun sake faruwa a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Sarauniya (Her Majesty's Secret Service) kuma sun sadu da Ophelia Bulletova, wata budurwa mai ban sha'awa da ta maye gurbin Olga Kurylenko.
A wani ɓangare kuma, firaministan ya faɗa cikin haɗarin wani attajiri da ya ce zai magance matsalar ɓarnar da ke damun ƙasar Britaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya yi wa barazana.
Tafiya ta ƙwarewa ta soma: English da Bough suna yin hidima a gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna kawo ƙanƙara sa'ad da suke gudu a kan jirgin ruwan Volta; English kuma yana kawo ƙanƙara sa'ad da yake gwada yadda za a yi amfani da na'urorin Virtual Reality don ya fahimci tsarin gidan Volta.
Ana kawar da duk wani abin da ke nuna cewa ana yin wasan kwaikwayo na ƙarshe, amma duk da cewa yana da kyau kuma yana da ban sha'awa a wannan yanayin, batun yara ya kasance a cikin labarin.
Yanayi ya ɗan daidaita.
Kamar sauran fina-finan Johnny English, ina tunanin: shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta ba Rowan Atkinson damar yin aiki a wani wuri da zai ba ta damar yin amfani da kwarewarta yadda ya kamata ba?
