Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma shin ya yi wani abu game da rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a birnin New York, wanda ke ɗauke da wasu mawaƙa da yawa da suke yin waƙa a kowace shekara, kuma yana ɗauke da babban maƙasudi na kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai tara dubun dubatan mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba wai kawai don sauraron wakokin masu kida kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don sanar da jama'a game da tasirin wannan waƙar don kawar da talauci kafin shekara ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen Festival, wanda aka kafa a shekara ta 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani rukunin duniya da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar yin amfani da mutane da yawa a wajen yaƙi da talauci.
Don a samu tikiti kyauta (sai dai idan kana son ka sayi tikitin VIP), masu son halartar taron suna bukatar su yi wasu ayyuka, ko kuma "ayyukan" kamar su ba da kansu don yin hidima, aika saƙon imel ga shugaban ƙasa, yin waya, ko kuma su yi wani aiki da zai sa a san cewa ana neman a kawar da talauci.
Amma, shin wannan shirin ya cim ma wani abu ne a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage kafin a cim ma burin da aka kafa?
Shin ba da tikiti kyauta ne zai sa mutane su yi mamaki ko kuma wani irin "hawan-hawan-hawan" ne - mutane su yi tunanin cewa suna yin wani abu ne ta wajen yin rajistar wani abu a dandalin sada zumunta ko kuma yin tweet?
Tun shekara ta 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta samu fiye da ayyuka miliyan 19 daga masu tallafa mata, suna neman a ƙara yin ayyuka.
Ya ce wannan aikin ya sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawarin ba da kuɗi da kuma ayyuka da suka kai dala biliyan 37 don su taimaka wa mutane biliyan 2.25 kafin shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ba da alkawura da sanarwa 390 game da ayyukansu, wanda kusan dala biliyan 10 aka tara kuma aka rarraba.
Ƙungiyar ta ce kuɗin da aka tara ya taimaka wa mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Ɗaya daga cikin waɗannan alkawarin shi ne The Power of Nutrition, wani kamfani na Ƙasar Ingila da ke "taimaka yara su yi girma yadda ya kamata", ya yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga ƙasar Rwanda don magance matsalar rashin abinci bayan da ta samu saƙonni 4,700 a Twitter daga 'yan ƙasa.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da agaji, gwamnatocin duniya, da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya yin aiki don tabbatar da rashin abinci a matsayin labari mai ban mamaki", in ji Tracey Ullman, mai wakiltar The Power of Nutrition ga taron masu sauraro a wani biki a London a watan Satumba na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an yi wa gwamnatin ƙasar Amirka fiye da 5,000 roƙo don ta inganta lafiyar mata da yara, sai ta ba da gudummawa ga shirin nan mai suna Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai wa mata da yara miliyan biyar da ke da lafiyar jiki.
Za ka iya amsa tambayar nan "Me ya sa kuke ganin za ku iya kawar da talauci?"
"Aiki ne mai wuya da kuma ɗaukan lokaci - muna faɗawa a wasu lokatai kuma za mu faɗawa", in ji Global Citizen.
Amma kamar yadda muke yi a dā, za mu yi nasara idan muka yi aiki tare.
Janet Jackson, Weekend, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin waɗanda za su yi waƙa a wannan shekara a birnin New York, inda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su yi waƙa.
Gwamnatin Amirka za ta iya yin amfani da Sojojin Ruwa a matsayin "garkuwa" don hana shigo da kayayyakin Rasha
Jaridar Washington Examiner ta ce, Washington za ta iya yin amfani da rundunar sojan ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don ta hana kayayyakin Rasha shiga kasuwancinta, har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya.
Zinke ya ce dangantakar Rasha da Siriya - wadda ya yi aiki a kai a kai a ƙarƙashin umurnin gwamnati - ba ta da amfani sosai.
"Ina tsammanin suna cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya don su tattauna game da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, da kuma kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
A wannan yanayin, bisa ga mai mulki, akwai hanyoyin da za a yi aiki.
"Amurka tana da iko, ta wurin rundunar sojan ruwa, ta tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku sun kasance a bude, kuma idan ya cancanta, ta rufe, don tabbatar da cewa kayayyakinsu ba su shiga cikin garuruwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke yana magana ne ga masu sauraro a wani taro da ƙungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wadda ta kira "muryar mai amfani da makamashi a Amirka.
Sun ci gaba da kwatanta yadda Washington ta bi da Rasha da kuma Iran.
"Ayyukan sun shafi kuɗi da Iran da Rasha suke yi, a kan su ko a kan su, su yi amfani da su da kyau kuma su maye gurbin mai", in ji su, suna kiran Rasha "mai cin hanci da rashawa" da ke dogara da mai mai amfani da man fetur.
Wannan furucin ya zo ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke ƙoƙarin ƙara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, don maye gurbin Rasha, don samun ƙarin kayayyaki ga masu amfani da Turai.
Saboda haka, gwamnatin Trump, har da Shugaba Donald Trump, suna kokarin tilasta wa Jamus ta fice daga aikin "ba a so" na aikin Nord Stream 2, wanda a cewar Trump, ya sanya Moscow da Berlin "a cikin bauta".
Moscow ta sha yin da'awar cewa aikin da ake yi na gina magudanar ruwa mai girma mai tsawon murabba'in mita biliyan 110 mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda ya kai dala biliyan 11, aikin kasuwanci ne.
A Kremlin, an ce abin da ya sa Washington ta ƙi yin wannan aikin shi ne domin tana da wata matsala a kasuwanci kuma tana nuna rashin adalci.
"Na yi imani cewa mun ƙi ra'ayin cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama makami na zalunci ba kuma masu amfani da shi dole ne su sami 'yancin zaɓan wanda za su ba su makamashi", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan matakin na gwamnatin Amurka ya jawo zargi daga Jamus da ke nuna sake yin wannan aikin.
Ƙungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), ta bukaci gwamnatin Amurka ta guji takunkumin da EU ta yi game da tattaunawar haɗin kai tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Na ga cewa babban matsala shi ne lokacin da babbar kasa ta shiga kuma ta lalata ikon da muke da shi na samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban hukumar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da Angela Merkel ta yi da Vladimir Putin, shugaban Rasha.
