Wanda Ya Tsara Yanar Gizo na Duniya Yana Shirya Yanar Gizo Mai Sauya Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya ƙirƙiri Intane, ya soma wani tsarin da zai iya cin nasara a kan Facebook, Amazon, da kuma Google.
Wani sabon abu da wannan masanin fasaha ya yi shi ne Inrupt, wani sabon kamfani da ke aiki da kayan aikin Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Tsarin Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da za su iya ganin bayanan da kuma lokacin da za su iya ganin bayanan.
A wata hira da ya yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi daɗi cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "ya zama na duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi hakan yanzu", in ji shi game da wannan kayan aiki.
"A cikin kwanaki na ƙarshe za a faɗi".
Wannan kayan aikin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar "wurin ajiyar bayanai na yau da kullum" ko kuma POD.
Ka sami tsari, ayyuka, jadawalin lokaci, ajiyar kiɗa da sauran kayan aikin mutum da ayyuka.
Wannan kayan aiki yana da wani irin cewa Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify za a iya samu a kan wannan shafi a lokaci guda.
Ba kamar yadda ake yin amfani da labaran da aka rubuta a cikin wannan kayan aiki ba, mai amfani ne zai zaɓi abin da zai nuna wa mutane.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan kayan aikin "sake ƙarfafa mutum ta wurin labarina".
Inrupt ya tsara, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, don samar da haɗin kai, ayyuka da kuma ƙwarewa don samar da kayan aiki na Solid ga kowa.
A yanzu haka, Berners-Lee da Bruce da wasu ma'aikatan tsaro da aka saya daga IBM suna cikin wannan kamfanin, kuma an gayyaci wasu ma'aikata su shiga cikin aikin, da kuma wasu da suka ba da kansu don yin amfani da lambar.
Daga wannan makon, masu ƙera na'urori a faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu na'urori da ke cikin dandalin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da "Facebook da Google ba game da yin wani sabon canji da zai iya kawo sauyi a cikin kasuwancin su a cikin ɗan lokaci.
"Kada mu nemi izini daga wurin su".
A wani jawabi da ya yi a kan Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne ba da iko ga 'yan kasuwa da kuma ayyuka da za su taimaka wajen kāre mutunci da kuma amfani da sabon dandalin Internet na Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo canji a tsarin sadarwa sa'ad da ya kafa wani kayan aiki na duniya, wato World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya yi magana sosai game da batun adalci a kan Intane.
Tun lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da zama Co-Founder da Shugaba na World Wide Web Consortium, wani kamfanin yanar gizo da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
