Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley yana jin 'rashin aiki' domin yanayin da ya samu
Wani ɗan wasan Olympics mai suna Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin ba ya da wani abu da zai yi wa kowa saboda yanayinsa game da aure - amma hakan ya ƙarfafa shi ya yi wani abu a duniya.
Wani matashi ɗan shekara 24 bai fahimci cewa "wasu ba su da hankali" har sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A wani jawabi da ta yi a shirin farko na rediyo na Radio 4 mai suna Desert Island Discs, wadda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ta ce tana magana ne game da 'yancin ma'aurata da suke son su samu "bege".
Ya kuma ce yin wasan motsa jiki ya sa ya rage damuwa game da neman nasara a gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta daɗe tana gudanar da wannan taron, ta yi wata ɗaya a hutunta don rashin lafiya.
Da yake ya yi kama da wanda ba shi da aiki a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙanƙanta" a lokacin da yake girma domin "ba a yarda da mutane su so 'yan mata da maza ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan ra'ayin na ƙasƙanci da kuma na musamman, yana cikin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da kuma motsawa na yi wani abu a duniya".
Yana so ya tabbatar da cewa shi ma "mai-rai ne", kamar yadda ya ce, don kada ya sa wasu su ji kunya sa'ad da suka fahimci wasu abubuwa game da halittunsa.
Wani dan wasan da ya lashe lambar zinare biyu a gasar Olympics ya zama sanannen sanannen gay kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don yin kira ga sauran kasashe da su cire takunkumin da aka sanya wa ma'aurata masu luwadi.
Ya ce ya faɗi haka ne domin yana jin daɗin rayuwa cikin 'yanci daga matsi kuma yana son wasu su sami "bege".
Wani ɗan wasa da ya ci gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce ya taɓa yin soyayya da wani saurayi mai suna Dustin Lance Black, wani ɗan fim da ke Amirka, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekara ta 2013.
Daley ta auri wani ɗan wasan Oscar da ya girme ta da shekara 20 a wannan shekarar, amma ta ce wannan bambancin shekarun bai dame ta ba.
"Idan ka fuskanci irin wannan ƙalubale a lokacin ƙuruciyarka" - ta halarci gasar Olympics sa'ad da take 'yar shekara 14 kuma ta rasa mahaifinta bayan shekara uku - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani da ya fuskanci irin wannan ƙalubale a rana ɗaya, mai kyau da marar kyau.
A watan Yuni, suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce hakan ya canja "duk wani ra'ayinsa".
"Idan kun tambaye ni a bara, amsar da nake bayarwa ita ce koyaushe ina son lashe kofin zinare", in ji shi.
"Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare a gasar Olympics muhimmanci.
Yanzu, Robbie ne lambar zinariyar da na samu a gasar Olympics".
Ɗan ya sa wa mahaifinsa suna, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan da aka gano cewa yana da ciwon ƙwaƙwalwa.
