Jim Furyk, wanda shi ne ɗan wasan gaba, zai so ya sami 'yan wasa da yawa fiye da yadda zai iya yi a cikin tawagarsa, ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka sami uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk ya shiga cikin wannan juyin juya halin a ƙarshe, ya shiga cikin tawagar da ta yi nasara a Brooklyn kafin ya yi murna sa'ad da Turai ta yi "Mu'ujiza a Madinah".
