Girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa a ƙasar Indonesiya
Mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa da ta afkawa Palu ranar Alhamis, a cewar jami'an, kuma ana sa ran mutuwar za ta karu.
A lokacin da aka yi wa'adin, masu ba da agaji ba sa samun saƙo daga yankin Donggala, da ke arewacin Palu, kusa da inda girgizar ta afka.
A Palu, mutane 16,000 ne aka yi musu jinya a lokacin bala'in.
Ga wasu daga cikin waɗannan wuraren da ake kira Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, kuma yana da mazaunan mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da birnin yake bikin cika shekara 40 da samun 'yancin kai, sai girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa suka afka masa.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) da ke gabashin gabar tekun Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen da ke wannan yankin sun kai 299,200.
Aikin kamun kifi da noma suna da muhimmanci a tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Ƙungiyar Nickel tana da arziki a lardin, amma a Morowali, wani yanki da ke gaɓar tekun Sulawesi, ne ake samun mafi yawan nickel.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun yi wa Palu da Donggala barazana sosai, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a ƙasar Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa ta kashe mutane 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani guguwa kuma ya yi wa garin Donggala ambaliya a shekara ta 1996, kuma mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Wannan shi ne jerin girgizar ƙasa da kuma guguwa da suka fi ƙarfin da aka taɓa gani a shekarun baya:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta auku a lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta jawo ambaliyar ruwa da ta shafi ƙasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar tekun Indiya, yawancinsu a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta auku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen watan Yuli da kuma farkon watan Satumba.
Dubban mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesiya, kuma ta jawo ambaliyar ruwa a gaɓar tekun, ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane wajen 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon kafa 10 da suka halaka ƙauyuka da yawa da kuma kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta kawo bala'i da damuwa yayin da mutane suka tuna da bala'in girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa na 2004.
Ba a sami ambaliyar ruwa a lokacin ba, amma sama da mutane 100 sun rasa rayukansu a sakamakon ambaliyar.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa Lombok, babban birnin yawon buɗe ido na ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka gine-gine da yawa kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido da ba su da gidaje.
