Masu gabatar da kara a kotu suna neman a yanke masa hukuncin kisa a kan wanda ake zargin da kai harin a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York suna neman a hukunta Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York - hukuncin da ba a taɓa hukunta shi ba a wannan batun tun shekara ta 1953.
An yi zargin cewa Saipov, ɗan shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar Home Depot wajen yin wannan haɗarin a kan titin mota a kan titin mota a kan titin mota a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu kekuna a watan Maris da Maris.
Don a zartar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "a wurin" kuma ya yi wa wasu rauni "a wurin", in ji wani takardar neman hukuncin kisa da aka rubuta a Kudancin New York.
A waɗannan shari'o'in, ana iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa, bisa ga dokar kotu.
Makonni bayan haɗarin, wata hukuma ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa a kan abubuwa 22 da suka haɗa da kisa guda takwas da taimakon masu cin hanci da rashawa, wanda ake yawan amfani da shi a matsayin mai ba da shawara a shari'ar masu laifi, da kuma lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "shirye -shirye da kuma shiri sosai", in ji lauya, wanda ya kwatanta yanayin da Saipov ya bi da shi a matsayin "mugu, marar tausayi, da kuma na zalunci".
"Safiulo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa iyalin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da kuma Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, baƙin ciki, da kuma rashi", in ji wannan sanarwa.
Biyar cikin mutanen da aka bincika baƙi ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009 amma an canja hukuncinsa zuwa rai da mutuwa.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a jihar New York, bayan an kama su da laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Ƙari shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe Rosenbergs da kuma wasu a cikin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
