Red Tide: Ragewa a Pinellas, Manatee, da kuma Sarasota
Sabon bayani daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Florida ya nuna cewa Red Tide yana raguwa a wasu wurare a Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana samun raguwar yawan masu cutar a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier - wanda ke nufin cewa sun ragu.
Red Tide ya yi tafiyar mil 130 daga bakin teku daga yankin Pinellas zuwa yankin Lee da ke kudu maso yamma.
Ana iya samun filayen a kusan mil 10 daga yankin Hillsborough County, amma sun fi na wannan makon.
Red Tide kuma ya bayyana a Pasco County.
An ba da rahoton ƙarancin ƙarancin a Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙarancin zuwa sama a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, ƙarancin a Manatee County, a gabar tekun Sarasota County, ƙarancin a Charlotte County, ƙarancin a gabar tekun ko a Lee County, da ƙarancin a cikin Collier County.
An yi tawaye da mutane da yawa da aka ba da rahotonsu a gundumar Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier.
Ba a taɓa samun wani haɗari da aka yi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata ba.
